    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA303-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu vēṭkai tāṅkakillāḷāyt tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
            2. ciṟaippuṟattāṉ eṉpatu malintatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is what SHE said to the confidante, being one who did not endure the desire.
            2. It is also how she rejoiced at his being behind the fence.</p>
        </div>
      <div xml:id="NA303">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            oliyavin taṭaṅkiya yāma naḷḷeṉak</l>
<l>            kalikeḻu pākkan tuyiṉmaṭin taṉṟē</l>
<l>            toṉṟuṟai kaṭavuḷ cērnta parārai</l>
<l>            maṉṟap peṇṇai vāṅkumaṭaṟ kuṭampait</l>
<l>            tuṇaipuṇa raṉṟi luyavukkural kēṭṭoṟun</l>
<l>            tuñcāk kaṇṇa ṭuyaraṭac cāay</l>
<l>            namvayiṉ varuntu naṉṉuta leṉpa</l>
<l>            tuṇṭukol vāḻi tōḻi teṇkaṭal</l>
<l>            vaṉkaip paratava riṭṭa ceṅkōṟ</l>
<l>            koṭumuṭi yavvalai pariyap pōkkik</l>
<l>            kaṭumura ṇeṟicuṟā vaḻaṅku</l>
<l>            neṭunīrc cērppaṉṟa ṉeñcat tāṉē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l rend="indent2">Deep at midnight when sound has ceased [and] become still,</l>
<l>the bustling village has sunk into sleep.</l>
<l>Is there word, oh friend,</l>
<l rend="indent">of [her of] good forehead, suffering at our side,</l>
<l rend="indent">exhausted, for misery kills [her], her eyes not sleeping,</l>
<l rend="indent2">whenever she hears the suffering voice of the Aṉṟil,</l>
<l rend="indent2">united with [its] mate</l>
<l rend="indent2">in the nest on the bending stems of the palmyra tree</l>
<l rend="indent2">on the village common,</l>
<l rend="indent3">with [its] large trunk joined of old by the god</l>
<l>– in the heart of the man from the coast of the long water himself,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the dashing shark wanders, of fierce antagonism,</l>
<l rend="indent3">let off when the pretty net with bent knots was torn</l>
<l rend="indent4">from the straight rod held by strong-handed fishermen?</l>
       </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
